Product Description
Have you ever been shocked by touching a doorknob? Do you know what causes the shock? This nonfiction book, Static Electricity and Lightning, explains static electricity and how it relates to lightning. Includes a glossary of bold-faced vocabulary words, reading activities, an index of terms, and an answer key. Reading Level: 4, Fountas and Pinnell: Level U, Interest Level: 3Ã¢â‚¬â€œ7. The high-interest, informational text is leveled to the respected Fountas and Pinnell Guided Reading leveling system to ensure a young reader's success.
